{"title":"Potion of sleeping/zh-CN","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Potion_of_sleeping/zh-CN","type":"markdown","data":"**NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！**  \n[了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki](/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN \"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\")\n\n**[English](/wiki/Potion_of_sleeping \"Potion of sleeping\")** • [中文（中国大陆）‎]()\n\n| ! [![Pink potion.png](/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png)](/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png) |                                                                                                                              |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| 名称                                                                               | 沉睡                                                                                                                           |\n| 外观                                                                               | [随机](/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"随机外观 (page does not exist)\")             |\n| 基础价                                                                              | 100 [zm](/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81 \"金币\")                                                                                      |\n| 重量                                                                               | 20                                                                                                                           |\n| 怪物使用                                                                             | *怪物会将其用作[攻击物品](/index.php?title=%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"攻击物品 (page does not exist)\")。* |\n\n**沉睡药水**（potion of sleeping）是[NetHack](/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")中的一种[药水](/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"药水\")。\n\n[ ]\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 生成](#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90)\n- [2 描述](#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0)\n- [3 消息](#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF)\n- [4 百科文本](#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC)\n- [5 另请参阅](#.E5.8F.A6.E8.AF.B7.E5.8F.82.E9.98.85)\n- [6 引用及注释](#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A)\n\n## 生成\n\n[巫师](/index.php?title=%E5%B7%AB%E5%B8%88\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"巫师 (page does not exist)\")起始物品中的随机药水里有可能出现沉睡药水。\n\n## 描述\n\n[饮用](/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"饮用 (page does not exist)\")沉睡药水会让饮用者进入[睡眠](/index.php?title=%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"睡眠 (page does not exist)\")状态，状态的持续时长根据药水的[BUC](/index.php?title=BUC/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"BUC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")而定。祝福的药水持续13～23回合，未诅咒的药水持续25～35回合，诅咒的药水持续37～47回合。\n\n如果玩家持有[睡眠抵抗](/index.php?title=%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%8A%B5%E6%8A%97\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"睡眠抵抗 (page does not exist)\")或[自由行动](/index.php?title=%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"自由行动 (page does not exist)\")特质，则沉睡药水对其无效[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)。\n\n怪物会[投掷](/index.php?title=%E6%8A%95%E6%8E%B7\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"投掷 (page does not exist)\")沉睡药水攻击玩家。吸入沉睡药水的[蒸汽](/index.php?title=%E8%92%B8%E6%B1%BD\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"蒸汽 (page does not exist)\")会使玩家进入持续1～5回合的睡眠状态，并[损害](/index.php?title=%E6%8D%9F%E5%AE%B3\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"损害 (page does not exist)\")敏捷[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2)。被沉睡药水击中的怪物则会陷入持续1～12回合的睡眠状态，除非怪物有睡眠抵抗[\\[3\\]](#cite_note-3)。\n\n## 消息\n\n- 你打呵欠。（You yawn.）\n\n  你受到了沉睡药水的影响，但因具有睡眠抵抗或自由行动，免疫了其效果。\n\n- 你感觉非常的累。（You feel rather tired.）\n\n  你受到沉睡药水蒸汽的影响。\n\n- <怪物>睡着了。（\\<monster> falls asleep.）\n\n  怪物受到了沉睡药水的影响。\n\n## 百科文本\n\n沉睡药水的百科文本与[酒](/wiki/%E9%85%92 \"酒\")相同。\n\nOn waking, he found himself on the green knoll whence he had first seen the old man of the glen. He rubbed his eyes -- it was a bright sunny morning. The birds were hopping and twittering among the bushes, and the eagle was wheeling aloft, and breasting the pure mountain breeze. \"Surely,\" thought Rip, \"I have not slept here all night.\" He recalled the occurrences before he fell asleep. The strange man with a keg of liquor -- the mountain ravine -- the wild retreat among the rocks -- the woe-begone party at ninepins -- the flagon -- \"Oh! that flagon! that wicked flagon!\" thought Rip -- \"what excuse shall I make to Dame Van Winkle!\"\n\n\\[ Rip Van Winkle, a Posthumous Writing of Diedrich Knickerbocker, by Washington Irving ]\n\n## 另请参阅\n\n- [麻痹药水](/index.php?title=%E9%BA%BB%E7%97%B9%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"麻痹药水 (page does not exist)\")\n- [冥想](/index.php?title=%E5%86%A5%E6%83%B3\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"冥想 (page does not exist)\")\n\n## 引用及注释\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.4.3, line 611](/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/src/potion.c#line611 \"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/src/potion.c\")\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.4.3, line 1263](/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/src/potion.c#line1263 \"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/src/potion.c\")\n3. [↑](#cite_ref-3) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.4.3, line 1062](/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/src/potion.c#line1062 \"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/src/potion.c\")\n\n[![此条目可能需要根据NetHack的最新版本进行修订。详细信息请点击此处。](/images/b/b0/Nh343-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"此条目可能需要根据NetHack的最新版本进行修订。详细信息请点击此处。\")\n\n**本页面可能需要根据NetHack的[最新版本](/wiki/Current_version \"Current version\")进行修订。**\n\n条目中可能含有仅适用于[NetHack 3.4.3](/wiki/NetHack_3.4.3 \"NetHack 3.4.3\")的过时信息。\n\n**致编辑者：**对条目进行必要的编辑及审阅后，请将{{nethack-343}}模板中的版本号改为最新版本的版本号，或根据实际需要，将模板替换为{{noversion}}。\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Potion of sleeping/zh-CN - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgC